Elfin magic. Elves made the iris, so it's indestrooctible!

Actually, the going theory is that the iris, being situated so close to the emitting fields of the Stargate, prevent that overpressure wave from forming in the first place, and it is the movement of that wave that would disintegrate matter.

Akin to the waterhead behind a dam. Given enough room to accelerate and attain momentum, the mass of water in a reservoir could easily smash the dam and everything downriver of it—but only if it is given enough room to accelerate in the first place...
